{# ── PROCESS ── #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="section-label">How It Works</span>
      <h2>From Brief to Live</h2>
      <p>Most sites are live in 2–3 weeks. Here's how we get there.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-list" style="margin-top: var(--s12);">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__num">01</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="process-step__title">Discovery</h3>
          <p class="process-step__desc">We talk about your aesthetic, your goals, your current digital presence, and what you want the site to do. Reference sites, design direction, content needs — all gathered upfront.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__num">02</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="process-step__title">Content Collection</h3>
          <p class="process-step__desc">Bio, photos, music links, tour dates, merch — we collect what exists and identify what needs to be created. We write copy if needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__num">03</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="process-step__title">Build</h3>
          <p class="process-step__desc">Design and development happen in one pass. We build the full site, integrate all platforms, and QA across devices before you see it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__num">04</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="process-step__title">Review & Launch</h3>
          <p class="process-step__desc">You review, we revise. One round of revisions is included. Once approved, we deploy to GitHub Pages and connect your domain. Live in minutes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-step__num">05</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="process-step__title">Handoff & Support</h3>
          <p class="process-step__desc">We document how to update content, manage tour dates, and handle the merch store. Ongoing maintenance available if you'd rather not touch it yourself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

